<para style="p">A psalm of David.</para>

<para style="b" />

<para style="q1">

<verse number="1" style="v" />To you, Yahweh, I lift up my life!</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="2" style="v" />My God, I trust in you.</para>

<para style="q1">Do not let me be humiliated;</para>

<para style="q1">do not let my enemies rejoice triumphantly over me.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="3" style="v" />May no one who hopes in you be disgraced</para>

<para style="q1">may those who act treacherously without cause be ashamed!</para>
